7.5: Primarily an on-premise focused release, though it began the "warp speed"
effort to match features with FICO Decision Modeler (the cloud version).

7.6: Further bridged the gap between the on-premise IDE and the cloud.
It optimized the Deployment Wizard to make it easier to package rules as Decision Services that
